name: HKMetricPrefix
desc: Prefixes that can be added to SI units to change the order of magnitude.

items.name: case none
items.desc: A prefix that does not modify the base unit.

items.name: case femto
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 1e-15.

items.name: case pico
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 1e-12.

items.name: case nano
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 1e-9.

items.name: case micro
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 1e-6.

items.name: case milli
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 0.001.

items.name: case centi
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 0.01.

items.name: case deci
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 0.1.

items.name: case deca
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 10.

items.name: case hecto
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 100.

items.name: case kilo
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 1000.

items.name: case mega
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 1e6.

items.name: case giga
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 1e9.

items.name: case tera
items.desc: A prefix that multiplies the base unit by 1e12.
